match_intro: H&H Export will face off against CD Walter Ferretti in a Primera Division match at Estadio Municipal de Matucana on January 31, 2026 GMT.

In an upcoming I Liqa clash on February 12, 2026, at Baku Sporting, the home team, Baku Sporting, currently positioned 2nd in the league standings, with 26 points, will face off against the 7th-placed MOIK Baku, with 15 points, in an intriguing encounter.
